   </teiHeader> <text type="letter"> <body><div type="writingSession" n="1"><p>Circa <date>20ten</date> hoffe ich wir fahren <rs ref="#pmb30" type="place">Salzburg</rs>–<rs ref="#pmb33929" type="place">Lofer</rs>–<rs ref="#pmb867" type="place">Innsbruck</rs>– (Seitenausflug <rs ref="#pmb607" type="place">Stubaital</rs>)–<rs ref="#pmb608" type="place">Brenner</rs>–<rs ref="#pmb987" type="place">Toblach</rs> (Seitenausflug <rs ref="#pmb39757" type="place">Ampezzotal</rs>)–<rs ref="#pmb41052" type="place">Spital a. Drau</rs>–<rs ref="#pmb41035" type="place">Radstadt</rs>–<rs ref="#pmb41003" type="place">Bischofshofen</rs>–<rs ref="#pmb30" type="place">Salzburg</rs>, circa 1–2 Tage.</p><p><salute>lieber, </salute>falls aber in <rs ref="#pmb30" type="place">Salzburg</rs> schönes, wirklich sommerliches Wetter, mit dem Character des Bleibenden sein sollte, so telegraphieren Sie mir sogleich.</p><closer>Ihr<signed>Hugo</signed></closer></div></body> </text></TEI>